then user click on Explore All Vehicles
and user checks Gas checkbox
then user should see text under Future Vehicles "Please reset to see Future Vehicles" and  

US4
background user is ford page ford.com
when user clicks on suvs& crossovers
then user click on Explore All Vehicles
and user checks Gas checkbox
then Future Vehicles checkbox is disabled 

US5
